软件包 com.generaterequest

类摘要
CreateVM This class is the base class for creating VM requests.
CreateVMByEndTime A decorator class for CreateVM.java, requests are produced by end time in decreasing order.
CreateVMByPorcessTime Using the Decorate Pattern to change the rule for producing requests by processing time in descending order.
PMBootor This class is used to acquire the number of each kind of PMs from the local configuration file.
RequestGenerator This class is used to load requests information from vmRequest.txt file into a VirtualMachine arraylist.
